Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
Come to think of it, have you ever had your first dream？
I still haven't seen it...
I dreamt of having a date, ▲小早川＊▲...
Hmm, I see. Rinko haven't seen it either. I thought I'd at least hear what you had to say.
So, should we look forward to next year？
I don't mind you saying that... You know, it's because... you have those dreams because you love me.
Rinko
Don't you think this cold is too harsh these days, ▲主人公＊▲？
I won't say it's harsh because we are on winter.
Who decided that winter is cold？ That's outrageous. There is nothing good about it being cold.
Snow is romantic, right？
If it's cold, we can warm each other up, right？
What, a romantic guess？ ...That kind of thing might be nice... But, I could do without the cold.
What, you want to hold hands... or something？ Rinko doesn't mind. Here, hold my hand.
Rinko
Do you know there's a plum tree blooming by the street I walk to school？ It's just down a side street, ▲主人公＊▲.
I didn't notice that at all.
So here's a quiz. Do you know the language of plum blossoms？
A noble heart！
Plum are plums！
Ah, good answer. Rinko just happened to learn about it yesterday....
By the way, it's still cold even though the plums are in bloom. Ah, geez, it's so cold！
Rinko
There's cherry blossom trees behind the school. I saw them from the window of the school building the other day, and they say now is the best time to see them.
I see. That's a good place for cherry blossom viewing because only students go near there.
So, you know, a friend of mine in my class wanted to see you, so she asked me if you wanted to go to Cherry Blossom Viewing with her.
No, I want it to be just the two of us！
I'd at least show up
No... What are you saying？ You sly old man, hehe！
Oh, you're embarrassed. Well, Rinko is embarrassed too, even if she really comes.
You're yawning a lot... are you bored, perhaps？
Rinko
No, I'm just sleepy. See, it's been warmer lately, so it's hard to get up in the morning.
That's true. I often get sleepy in class.
You too？ I wonder why you are so sleepy.
It's like spring sleep, but you ignore when dawn comes
Because you're in my dreams ▲小早川＊▲...
That's not a reason... and more importantly, what do you mean... Don't say that with a smug look on your face！
Is that your reason？ That doesn't really apply to Rinko... Because that only comes up once in a while.
Rinko
Oh, I didn't know there was a flower bed here. These tiny flowers are cute...
Do you like flowers, ▲小早川＊▲？
It's superfluous... So, what kind of flowers go with Rinko？
Glamorous flowers！
A neat and tidy flower, perhaps？
Heh, that might be a little surprising. Glamorous, huh... That's a good thing, right？
I'm a little unsure about it, but... actually might not feel too bad about it.
Rinko
I was looking at my calendar, and I realized a crucial fact, ▲主人公＊▲.
What was it... I don't think I skipped on a date, did I？
If you did that, I would kick you immediately. No, I mean, this year is already half over... Don't you think it went too fast？
That's how fulfilling it was！
We still have the other half, right？
I see, maybe... Ah, so it's your fault that it went by so fast？ Yes, should I kick you？
Hah, that positive attitude is so nice. No, no, Rinko needs to learn from you！
Rinko
I thought summer vacation was long, but it goes by so fast.
Still haven't had enough fun？
Well, maybe... Anyway, what about your homework？
Of course it's over！
Don't tell me that you ▲小早川＊▲...
Bummer. I could have made fun of you if you hadn't already. Even though Rinko took this seriously.
Too bad, Rinko finished it already. You're the one who asked, so could it be that you...？
Rinko
Have you prepared for a change of clothes？ You're so early, you've changed into winter clothes, ▲主人公＊▲.
I see... it's already autumn.
You're looking far away. What are you thinking？
Because in autumn, girls aren't wearing as much light clothing！
I miss my summer memories.
You're the worst！ At least if it was "girlfriend" instead of "girl" it would have been more cute！
Yes, well... But you know, I'm sure you'll make many new memories in the fall. I'm sure I'll make a lot of new memories with you...
Rinko
If you've changed your clothes, that means it's already fall, okay？ Is that right？
It's already fall on the calendar.
Then why is it so hot？ It's abnormal weather, that's why. Global warming is serious.
You're overreacting, you'll get by！
Maybe you're getting eco- friendly？
That kind of consciousness ruins the environment... Personally, I don't mind that kind of thing.
No, Rinko will be running the air conditioner as hard as she can, so you'll have to be patient and save energy instead.
Rinko
October is Kannazuki in the lunar calendar.
A moon without God, right？
So you knew. Are you good at ancient literature？
I used it as a mnemonic！
I just have a lot of random knowledge
Ah, so that's what it was. You remember it without knowing what it means, but I wonder if that's okay.
Even if you can't study anything, knowing something like that makes you look smart. So you can do that too...
Rinko
It was freezing this morning, and the puddle in front of my house was frozen, ▲主人公＊▲.
It suddenly got cold. It's already winter.
I hate the cold, but isn't it fun to hear the crisp sound of stepping on that thin ice？
Isn't that childish？
I know that feeling！
It's okay. This is not childish, it's called innocence！
Right～？ It's a silly, little pleasure.
Rinko
They often do animal shows on TV, but I think that kind of thing is easy.
What do you mean easy？
They think that if they put out a baby animal or something, people will squeal at them.
It's a great way to get ratings...
So, you don't watch those, ▲小早川＊▲？
Good grief, it's tough being an adult. Dad is also struggling with the audience rating...
I didn't say that. It's vexing, but baby animals are not good.
Even Rinko will get excited.
Rinko
What's your favorite animal？ I never asked you, did I？
Oh, is that right？
Let me know. It's called boyfriend research.
I like dogs
I like cats
Hmmm. Well, each person has his or her own preference. It's not like Rinko doesn't like dogs.
Really？ I hope I'm not forcing you to fit in.
Well, next time I see a cat, I'll let you fluff it up too.
Rinko
My parents are planning a playdate. The destination is the zoo... What do you think？
Hmm, why not？ It would be fun to go with the family.
Heh, to that kind of play, why？
They're recreating the ecosystem！
I like the direct interaction！
Hmm, you mean you're going to study？ Well, I don't want my brother to hate studying like Rinko.
I see... It does feel like a family gathering, doesn't it？ Well, I'll go along with you.
Rinko
I've been getting pointed at a lot lately in English class, and I'm pretty sure they're looking at Rinko like an enemy！
Did you have a problem with your English sensei？
Once, he complimented me on my English pronunciation. Thanks to that, I have to read every time. It annoys me that they think I can speak English just because I listen to Western music.
Sounds tough...
That's a good thing, don't you think？
Right？ Just because I like English songs doesn't mean I like English classes.
I don't feel bad about getting compliments, but... it's hard to keep up with expectations.
Rinko
I saw a young, beautiful woman in the staff room the other day. Guess who it was？
Hmm, I don't know.
Apparently, she is a former student of the Principal. It looks like she's coming to our school for an internship.
A sensei, huh... I might admire her a little bit.
You want to be a sensei ▲小早川＊▲！？
Maybe you're a better sensei than you think
What？ You'd be surprised what a good sensei even Rinko can be, don't you think？ No homework, no tests. Now that's a big hit with the students.
It was supposed to be a joke... And when you're a sensei, you can't skip class.
Rinko
Why is there such a thing as uniforms？ How many centimeters is the length of the skirt, and how much is too much？
The noisy ones are the life guidance senseis, right？ It's true that there are school rules, but they're a little too detailed.
The senseis doesn't tell the boys that much.
Hah, I wish I could go to school in plain clothes. Don't you think so？
I'd rather wear plain clothes
I prefer the uniform
Well, that's easy. And you get to see your girlfriend in various outfits！
...Oh, so that's the kind of fetish you have. Please don't look at me in a weird way, okay？
Rinko
Lately, it seems that more and more students are making their own lunches.
Are you unsatisfied, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko's special place on the patio... Lately, it's been occupied by a couple.
It's a precious place where I can read a book in peace. They shouldn't be flirting at school.
Why don't you at least allow them a lunch break？
Do you want to make out too？
Umm... No, I can't do it. I can't have them flirting with me on the side.
No.pe！ It's like we're being swept along. If it was of our own volition, I wouldn't mind.
Rinko
How often do you lend or borrow notes before an exam？
Often enough. I get copies of notes from diligent people.
You know, I have a friend who takes very clear and neat notes. I guess that kind of thing is based on your sense.
I wonder. Some guys are easier to understand more than a reference book, right？
Rinko can't do that.
It's enough if you know what you're doing
Why don't you try to write carefully？
Oh, I see. If the notebooks you show me are clean, that's all right.
It's not like my notes are messy. Oh, and please show me your notes, senpai. For reference.
Rinko
I think my friend started a diet. So, I told her Rinko doesn't need to diet, and she told me she was jealous.
Certainly, even though you love to eat junk food, you never get fat, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hmmm, Rinko is just being normal. Why is everyone so desperate？
You shouldn't say that too often
I guess they want to be as pretty as possible
Too late for that advice. I got a lot of flack when I said it. It was difficult.
I don't think being thin is the same as being that. Even if you only take care of your appearance in the first place. Right？
Rinko
My friend is worried about her boyfriend cheating on her. She doesn't want to break up with him, but she doesn't know what to do.
Hmm...
Her boyfriend seems to be saying that men are cheating wimps... You're not, are you？
I wouldn't be too sure...！
Absolutely, I will not cheat！
...You wanna get kicked！？ No jokes that can't be laughed at！
Hmm, well said. Hehe... You will stay by Rinko's side forever and ever, won't you？
Rinko
Yesterday, my friend and I got into a little argument about which flavor of potato chips is the best.
...Is that what you're fighting about？
There is no way that consomme flavor's the best. Uzushio flavor is the best. It is the simplicity that makes the most of the flavors of the ingredients that is important.
I like all the flavors
You're a maniac, ▲小早川＊▲
If you say that, it's the end of the world. Some things in this world have to be black and white！
Hmmm, I guess so. You mean the times haven't caught up with Rinko？
Rinko
Should I have many friends, ▲主人公＊▲？
Eh, did something happen？
Not really, but you say that a lot. Make lots of friends.
...Well, most adults would say that.
There are a few girls I talk to a lot... but I'm not sure about how many.
If it's just numbers, don't think it means anything
Sometimes I get anxious, too
That's right. Rinko thinks so, too. If you say so, it's okay.
I see. I'm just a little relieved. I don't mind being anxious as long as I'm not alone.
Rinko
The other day, I went to karaoke with friends... Ah, geez.
What's wrong？
When I told them it was Western music only, they refused.
...I guess they don't want a song they don't know.
It's also a chance to meet new masterpieces. Everyone is so conservative.
You're so radical, ▲小早川＊▲
I wish you would have invited me.
I see. Culture is something to be actively enjoyed. If you listen only to what comes into your ears, your sensibilities will be corrupted.
Yeah... I have a song I'm practicing... We'll play it when we get good at it, right？
You seem to be in a good mood. What's up？
Rinko
At the arcade in front of the station, I met a powerful enemy.
Ah, fighting games.
And at the same age as Rinko... I knew having a rival would make me even stronger.
Sorry for not being a good rival
Is your rival perhaps a man？
I know you are not perfect. All I need is a perfect boyfriend.
It's a girl, okay？ Ah... I see, is that what you mean？ Do you think a male rival will show up～？
Rinko
Recently, I've been hooked on online auctions again. It really gets me excited.
Auctions, huh, that sounds interesting.
It's all about the tactics, and it's similar to a competitive fighting game.
What are you after now？
What's the biggest loot？
I'd like to get the Killer Bambies bootleg... I mean the pirate version, but I don't want to... It's bad for the artist.
There's a pick by the guitar god, God Mt. The scratches on it are raw～！
Rinko
I've been going to the city library lately and it's been better than I expected.
Yes, the library collection seems to be larger than the school's.
Not simply the number, but also the quality, I guess.
Hmm.
Recently, I've been trying to read fairy tales in the original book. It's not easy to do so in the school library.
You're very studious
A fairy tale？ Surprising
It's what I like to do. That's why I didn't think of it as studying.
I like fairy tales quite a bit, you know？
Just... don't tell anyone else because I don't want to be misunderstood.
Rinko
My friend's boyfriend is into martial arts these days.
Then, we can talk about it ▲小早川＊▲.
It's not that I'm a martial arts fan.
And yet she misunderstood and asked me if I wanted to go on a double date at the next martial arts event.
Could be interesting, huh？
I thought you would go all out ▲小早川＊▲...
You think？ But... it's not so much about martial arts, but about double-dating... I'm kind of nervous about it？
If you want, I can go wild now, you know？ Come on, here comes a kick, okay？
Rinko
Why are movies such a staple of dating, ▲主人公＊▲？
Isn't it because it's easier to find common ground？ Especially when you just started dating.
Hmm, a safe answer. So, what's the best movie in the early stages of a relationship？
Laughing at a comedy！
A romantic film！
You have a point. First of all, you have to create an enjoyable atmosphere. It would be a disaster if we get a bad movie.
Again, a safe answer. But I don't like it when I see an ulterior motive.
Rinko
Do you think it's better to have a girly girlfriend ▲主人公＊▲？
What？ What's wrong？
My friend's boyfriend said so... And, I was wondering about you.
You're girly enough, ▲小早川＊▲？
Their choices！ I'm my own man！
...If someone other than you had said that, I would have said, "Don't talk nonsense！ I'm kicking you."
But I'm glad you're saying that because you really understand Rinko...
I see... I don't mind. I don't care anymore！
There's a new ice cream shop in front of the station. The girls in my class were making a fuss.
Rinko
Oh, I know！ It's where they sing, dance and perform, right？
Yes, yes, I'd like to go there.
But I hear it's very popular and there's quite a line, right？
Let's go later, after things settle down
Alright, let's get in line！
I agree, jumping on the bandwagon is a little bit of a no-no. I would rather buy ice cream at a convenience store than wait in line for hours.
Huh？ You're gonna have to wait in line. My bad～？ ...It was a joke. We might have fun while waiting in line.
Rinko
My favorite onesie is getting tight. I'm shocked.
Hmm, too bad, but I can't help it.
That's the one that you complimented me on before. I have some memories of it...
It's a sign of growth, so rejoice！
Let's make new memories！
Well, I see. I can keep it even if I can't wear it anymore！
...You're really positive. Now that you've said it, do it right, okay？ I'm still counting on you to do this.
Rinko
Hey, do you know how to write a love letter ▲主人公＊▲？
What！？
A friend of mine wants to confess her feelings, but she's too embarrassed to do it in person.
That girl better figure it out for herself
A direct confession is best ▲小早川＊▲
I know, right？ Yeah, I know. I was just asking, I'll tell her that.
Huh！？ Rinko had nothing to do with it！ You're an idiot.
Rinko
Did you know that the arcade in front of the station has a new gaming system ▲主人公＊▲？
Hmm, I didn't know.
That doesn't qualify you as Rinko's boyfriend, okay？ Get it？ The new machine is a brawler... are you listening to me？
I-I'm listening.
Hey. Maybe you don't like gaming？ If you don't like it, I won't talk about it anymore...
I'm not that interested in it
I like them, but that's technical stuff...
Yes, it's no fun if you keep losing to Rinko.
Ah, that's it. Let's train, shall we？ That way you'll be more interested！
What, you just don't have enough training. I'll give you some training. I'm going to work on that new one for now.
Rinko
We were going to throw a softball in gymnastics. My friend said, "Rinko can only throw it about 10 meters."
Even elementary kids could throw more...
Right？ You're too soft on Rinko, no matter how bad she is at sports. You've got to get serious.
Oh, you're unusually motivated！
I want to see a good record！
Yes, it's rare. If I look back at that girl, I'll linger in normal mode.
When you say that, I start to feel a little unsure. You know... will you come with me to practice？
Rinko
Mom decided to take my brother home with her for a while. So Rinko announced that she would take over all the housework. I did it on the spur of the moment.
So you can do housework ▲小早川＊▲...？
...I probably can do it. Well, my dad says Rinko doesn't have to do anything.
Your father is right
I guess I'll take this as an opportunity to learn to be a bride！
I'm pissed off at the way you put it... but well, I guess I'll at least start with the laundry. I don't know about cooking...
...Are you expecting something？ But hey, don't you think the term "bride training" is prehistoric？
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Hmm？ What？
What was that. Did I do something？
Nothing. I just thought that if you were guilty of something, you'd probably come clean.
...Yeah right, just kidding.
Hmmm, the second time.
I heard that you can tell the depth of affection by the number of times you call their name. I don't know if it's true or not.
Rinko
You know, have you ever wondered where your name comes from ▲主人公＊▲？
Em, I guess so...
Come to think of it, I've never cared
I was curious, so I asked my parents
Hmmm, is that what boys do？
Hehe, well, tell me. What does it mean？
Can you call my name ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yeah, I'm happy！
▲小早川＊▲！
Yes, yes, I thought that would be the case.
Rinko is kind enough to call you without saying anything, ▲主人公＊▲.
What is that, playing the idiot couple, are we？ Sometimes it's nice to do that. Is that a male trait？
